                                        text ever since the 1500s
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
                                <button type="button" class="btn bg-amber btn-block btn-lg waves-effect">
                                    With License
                                    <br />
                                    ₹ 1500/-
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3 pull-right">
                                <button type="button" class="btn bg-amber btn-block btn-lg waves-effect">
                                    Without License
                                    <br />
                                    ₹ 1000/-
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
